WEBVTT

00:01:27.741 --> 00:01:30.550
nain khulhrang in an ti ahcun,
zapi lakah an itel ve ko lai.

00:01:30.574 --> 00:01:33.306
(Nihthawng)

00:01:33.330 --> 00:01:34.845
Cuticun, 
minute tlawmpal hnuah,

00:01:34.869 --> 00:01:37.631
zapi lakah an ipeih 
thluahmah na hmuh lai

00:01:37.655 --> 00:01:40.916
itel ve lo tu kha an duh ti lai lo.

00:01:40.940 --> 00:01:42.917
Hihi cawlcanghnak thawkning cu asi.

00:01:42.941 --> 00:01:44.917
Asi, hi chungin cawnnak ilak u sih.

00:01:45.656 --> 00:01:47.976
Hmasaah, amah lawng in
a dir i ankgi loin a lammi

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:50.976
bantuk na si ahcun.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:54.976
Zultu hmasa pawl kha tlukruannak in 
na hruai hna aherh kha philh hlah.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:57.450
Afiang. Cawlcanghnak kong asi,
nangmah kong asi lo.

00:01:57.474 --> 00:01:58.536
(Nihthawng)

00:01:58.560 --> 00:02:01.076
Si, cawn/ilak ding taktak 
kan hrialh sual kho men.